OL,3,CMan due in court over Belfast knife
OL,4,Cattack following night of violence
OL,6,FA man is set to appear in court
OL,7,Fcharged with attempted murder over a
OL,8,Fstabbing attack following a night of
OL,9,Fviolence in Belfast.
OL,11,FSome people were forced to flee their
OL,12,Fhomes and multiple cars and homes were
OL,13,Fset alight in the disorder on Tuesday
OL,14,Fwhich followed Monday's knife attack
OL,15,Fin the north of the city.
OL,17,FThe 30-year-old accused, who is
OL,18,FSudanese, is also charged with
OL,19,Fpossession of an article with a blade
OL,20,For point in a public place and making
OL,21,Fthreats to kill.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
