PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781053389
OL,3,CMan due in court over Belfast knife
OL,4,Cattack following night of violence
OL,6,FHe is due to appear at Belfast
OL,7,FMagistrates' Court later on Wednesday.
OL,9,FFollowing widespread condemnation of
OL,10,Fthe incident, anti-immigration
OL,11,Fdemonstrations took place across
OL,12,FNorthern Ireland on Tuesday evening,
OL,13,Fwith a number descending into disorder.
OL,15,FA Glider bus was set alight in east
OL,16,FBelfast, prompting all bus and train
OL,17,Fservices to be suspended.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
