PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781053389
OL,3,CMan due in court over Belfast knife
OL,4,Cattack following night of violence
OL,6,FIn Lendrick Street in Belfast, several
OL,7,Fcars were set alight and Northern
OL,8,FIreland Fire and Rescue Service
OL,9,Fofficers had to remove some residents
OL,10,Ffrom houses after they caught fire.
OL,12,FA number of houses and vehicles were
OL,13,Fset on fire near the Ligoniel Road
OL,14,Farea of Belfast and a police car was
OL,15,Fset alight in Portadown.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
