PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781053389
OL,3,CMan due in court over Belfast knife
OL,4,Cattack following night of violence
OL,6,FPolice Service of Northern Ireland
OL,7,F(PSNI) Assistant Chief Constable Ryan
OL,8,FHenderson said officers had worked
OL,9,Falongside partner agencies "responding
OL,10,Fto incidents as they arise and helping
OL,11,Fto keep people safe".
OL,13,FPolitical leaders criticised Tuesday
OL,14,Fnight's violent scenes.
OL,16,FNorthern Ireland's First Minister
OL,17,FMichelle O'Neill condemned the
OL,18,F"outright thuggery".
OL,26,@qD@\OUsD@TO]zD@AOUzD@SO]
