PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781053389
OL,3,CMan due in court over Belfast knife
OL,4,Cattack following night of violence
OL,6,FShe said: "Groups of masked men
OL,7,Fburning families out of their homes is
OL,8,Fnothing less than disgusting
OL,9,Fcowardice."
OL,11,FDeputy First Minister Emma Little-
OL,12,FPengelly said: "Taking frustration at
OL,13,Fthe evil actions of a person out on
OL,14,Fthose who had no part in it is utterly
OL,15,Fwrong."
OL,26,@nD@KOUqD@KO]tD@POUwD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
