PN,30207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781053389
OL,3,CMan due in court over Belfast knife
OL,4,Cattack following night of violence
OL,6,FDetectives have said there is no
OL,7,Findication Monday's knife attack was
OL,8,Fterror-related.
OL,10,FThe PSNI has launched a "critical
OL,11,Fincident" in response to the incident
OL,12,Fwhich was captured on video and
OL,13,Fappears to show a man stabbing at the
OL,14,Fvictim's head and neck while he was
OL,15,Flying on the ground.
OL,26,@rD@YOUsD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
