PN,30208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781053389
OL,3,CMan due in court over Belfast knife
OL,4,Cattack following night of violence
OL,6,FThe clip shows people, including one
OL,7,Fwith a hurling stick, intervening to
OL,8,Fstop the man attacking the victim in
OL,9,Fthe Kinnaird Avenue residential area
OL,10,Fclose to the busy Antrim Road in north
OL,11,FBelfast.
OL,13,FA kitchen knife was recovered from the
OL,14,Fscene.
OL,16,FPolice revealed details on the
OL,17,Farrested man's immigration status and
OL,18,Fhow he travelled to the UK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
