PN,30209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781053389
OL,3,CMan due in court over Belfast knife
OL,4,Cattack following night of violence
OL,6,FHe entered Northern Ireland across the
OL,7,FIrish border in February 2023 having
OL,8,Fflown to Dublin from Paris.
OL,10,FThe suspect claimed asylum upon
OL,11,Farrival and in September 2023 was
OL,12,Fgranted leave to remain in the UK
OL,13,Funtil 2028.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/9
